        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-4 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/Features.astro:alur5y">25kVA – 50MVA</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/Features.astro:13ykra">Elsan Transformer is a Turkish-manufactured product line offering one of the broadest transformer ranges available in the Nigerian and West African market — from compact 25 kVA distribution units to heavy-duty 50 MVA power transformers. Engineered for 11kV and 33kV networks, the two most common voltage classes used by DISCOs and industrial operators across the region.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 2 -->
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 group" data-ps="src/components/home/Features.astro:item-2">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-slate-100 group-hover:border-[#E85D1A] transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/home/Features.astro:e0j4yk">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#E85D1A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.040L3 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622l-1-2.382z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-4 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/Features.astro:alur5z">ISO Certified</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/Features.astro:bf5cf2">Every Elsan transformer is manufactured under a rigorous quality management system certified to ISO 9001, ISO 14001, and ISO 45001 standards. From raw material selection to final assembly, each unit undergoes comprehensive routine testing before dispatch — so you receive equipment you can depend on from day one</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 3 -->
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 group" data-ps="src/components/home/Features.astro:item-3">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-slate-100 group-hover:border-[#E85D1A] transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/home/Features.astro:e0j4yj">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#E85D1A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a2 2 0 11-4 0V4zM11 14a2 2 0 114 0v1a2 2 0 11-4 0v-1zM11 19a2 2 0 114 0v1a2 2 0 11-4 0v-1zM5 10a2 2 0 114 0v1a2 2 0 11-4 0v-1zM17 10a2 2 0 114 0v1a2 2 0 11-4 0v-1z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-4 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/Features.astro:alur60">IEC 60076</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/Features.astro:bf5cf3">All Elsan power and distribution transformers are designed and tested in full compliance with IEC 60076 — the internationally recognised standard for power transformers. This guarantees consistent electrical performance, dielectric integrity, and long-term reliability across all operating conditions and grid environments in Nigeria and beyond</p>
